#ROOM
Vnum     14700
Name     &WDun Morogh - Southern Gate&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     Snow swirls around you as you stand at the southern entrance to &CDun
Morogh&d, the frozen mountain homeland of the Bronzebeard dwarves. The
massive gates of &YIronforge&d loom to the &Ynorth&d, their bronze surfaces
gleaming despite the frost. The road winds &Ysouth&d down into the frozen
wilderness, where troggs, trolls, and worse await the unwary.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14000
Desc      The great gates of Ironforge beckon.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14701
Desc      The road descends into the snowy wilderness.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14714 2 14700
  Reset E 1 14716 1 16
  Reset E 1 14717 1 12
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14701
Name     &WDun Morogh - Northern Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road cuts through deep snowdrifts as it winds between towering peaks.
Pine trees laden with snow line the path, their branches drooping under
the weight. The air is bitterly cold, and your breath fogs before you.
Ironforge lies to the &Ynorth&d, and the road continues &Ysouth&d toward
Kharanos.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14700
Desc      The road leads north toward Ironforge.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14702
Desc      The road continues south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14711 2 14701
Reset M 0 14723 3 14701
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14702
Name     &WDun Morogh - Misty Pine Refuge&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A small clearing among the ancient pines offers a brief respite from the
wind. The trees here are massive, their trunks wider than a dwarf is tall.
Mist drifts between the snow-covered branches, giving the area an ethereal
quality. The road continues &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d, and a trail leads &Yeast&d
into the deeper forest.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14701
Desc      The road leads north toward Ironforge.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14703
Desc      A trail leads into the misty forest.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14710
Desc      The road continues south toward Kharanos.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14722 2 14702
Reset M 0 14709 2 14702
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14703
Name     &WMisty Pine Woods&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The ancient pines grow thick here, blocking what little sunlight filters
through the clouds. Snow lies in deep drifts between the trees, and the
mist muffles all sound. It would be easy to become lost in this frozen
maze. The trail leads &Ywest&d back to the road, and continues &Yeast&d
deeper into the woods.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14704
Desc      The trail continues deeper into the woods.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14702
Desc      The trail leads back to the road.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14711 3 14703
Reset M 0 14712 1 14703
  Reset E 1 14704 1 16
Reset O 0 14710 2 14703
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14704
Name     &WIce Claw Cavern - Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A dark cave mouth yawns in the hillside, its entrance rimmed with icicles
as thick as a dwarf's arm. Wolf tracks and gnawed bones litter the snow
outside—this is clearly the den of the Ice Claw wolf pack. Snarls and
howls echo from within. The woods lie to the &Ywest&d, and the cave
continues &Yeast&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14705
Desc      The cave descends into darkness.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14703
Desc      The misty woods lie outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14711 3 14704
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14705
Name     &xIce Claw Cavern - Den&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The cave opens into a large chamber where the Ice Claw pack makes its
home. Bones of prey animals are scattered across the frozen floor, and
crude nests of dried grass line the walls. The alpha wolf watches from
a raised ledge, its pale eyes gleaming in the darkness.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14704
Desc      The cave entrance lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14712 1 14705
  Reset E 1 14704 1 16
Reset M 0 14711 4 14705
Reset O 0 14710 3 14705
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14710
Name     &WDun Morogh - Kharanos Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road widens here as it approaches the village of &YKharanos&d. You
can see smoke rising from chimneys to the &Ysouth&d, and the smell of
brewing ale carries on the wind. A signpost points &Ywest&d toward
Brewnall Village and &Yeast&d toward the Gol'Bolar Quarry.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14702
Desc      The road leads north toward Ironforge.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14740
Desc      The road leads toward Gol'Bolar Quarry.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14711
Desc      The village of Kharanos lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14730
Desc      The road leads toward Brewnall Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14714 1 14710
  Reset E 1 14716 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14711
Name     &YKharanos - North Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You enter &YKharanos&d, a bustling dwarven village nestled in the snowy
mountains. Stone buildings with smoking chimneys line the main street,
and the sound of hammering and laughter fills the air. The famous
&WThunderbrew Distillery&d dominates the town center to the &Ysouth&d.
Villagers go about their business despite the bitter cold.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14710
Desc      The road leads north into the mountains.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14712
Desc      The main square lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 3 14711
Reset M 0 14720 1 14711
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14712
Name     &YKharanos - Town Square&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The heart of Kharanos centers around a large stone well and the imposing
facade of the &WThunderbrew Distillery&d to the &Ywest&d. A general store
sits to the &Yeast&d, and the main road runs &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d. Despite
the cold, the square bustles with activity—merchants hawking wares,
children playing in the snow, and off-duty Mountaineers sharing tales.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14711
Desc      The north gate lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14714
Desc      The general store lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14713
Desc      The road continues south toward Coldridge Pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14715
Desc      The Thunderbrew Distillery beckons.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 4 14712
Reset M 0 14720 1 14712
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14713
Name     &YKharanos - South Road&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The road leaves Kharanos heading south toward &CColdridge Valley&d. A
small stable stands to the &Ywest&d, where mountain rams are tended. The
village square lies to the &Ynorth&d, and the road continues &Ysouth&d into
increasingly wild territory.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14712
Desc      The town square lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14720
Desc      The road leads south toward Coldridge Pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14716
Desc      The village stable lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 2 14713
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14714
Name     &YKharanos General Store&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small but well-stocked shop carries everything an adventurer might
need in the frozen wilderness. Warm cloaks, sturdy boots, dried rations,
and mining supplies line the shelves. A potbellied stove in the corner
keeps the shop warm, and the proprietor eyes you appraisingly.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14712
Desc      The town square lies outside.
~
