#ROOM
Vnum     14715
Name     &YThunderbrew Distillery - Taproom&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     The warmth hits you like a wave as you enter the famous &WThunderbrew
Distillery&d. A roaring fire crackles in an enormous hearth, and the air
is thick with the smell of hops, malt, and roasting meat. Dwarves crowd
around sturdy wooden tables, singing, arguing, and drinking the legendary
Thunderbrew Ale. A staircase leads &Ydown&d to the brewing floor.
~
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    14717
Desc      Stone stairs lead down to the brewing floor.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14712
Desc      The town square lies outside.
~
