Reset O 0 14714 3 14715
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14716
Name     &YKharanos - Village Stable&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The smell of hay and animal fills this sturdy stable. Mountain rams
stamp in their stalls, their thick wool keeping them warm even in the
unheated building. A handler tends to the beasts, ensuring they are fed
and healthy. Saddles and harnesses hang from hooks on the walls.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14713
Desc      The south road lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 1 14716
Reset M 0 14722 3 14716
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14717
Name     &YThunderbrew Distillery - Brewing Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Massive copper vats dominate this lower level, each one bubbling with
fermenting brew. The smell is overwhelming—a heady mix of yeast, grain,
and alcohol. Workers monitor temperatures, add ingredients, and tend the
fires that keep the process going. This is where the legendary Thunderbrew
Ale is born.
~
Exit
Direction up~
ToRoom    14715
Desc      The taproom lies above.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14719 1 14717
Reset M 0 14721 2 14717
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14720
Name     &WDun Morogh - Coldridge Pass North&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road climbs steeply as it enters &CColdridge Pass&d, the narrow route
connecting Kharanos to Coldridge Valley. Sheer cliffs rise on either side,
and snow-laden pines cling precariously to the slopes. The wind howls
through the pass, carrying flurries of ice. Kharanos lies to the &Ynorth&d,
and the pass continues &Ysouth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14713
Desc      The road leads back to Kharanos.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14721
Desc      The pass continues south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14709 2 14720
Reset M 0 14711 2 14720
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14721
Name     &WColdridge Pass - Summit&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     You stand at the highest point of Coldridge Pass. The view is breathtaking
despite the bitter cold—snowy peaks stretch in every direction, and you
can see the smoke of Kharanos to the &Ynorth&d and the distant lights of
Anvilmar to the &Ysouth&d. A narrow trail branches &Ywest&d toward a cave
rumored to house wendigos.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14720
Desc      The pass descends toward Kharanos.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14722
Desc      The pass descends toward Coldridge Valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14725
Desc      A treacherous trail leads toward Wendigo Cave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14714 1 14721
  Reset E 1 14716 1 16
  Reset E 1 14717 1 12
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14722
Name     &WColdridge Pass - South Descent&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road winds down through the final stretch of Coldridge Pass. The
cliffs begin to recede, and the valley opens before you. You can see the
frozen lake and small settlement of Coldridge Valley below. Trogg totems
mark territory dangerously close to the road.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14721
Desc      The pass leads back up to the summit.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14750
Desc      The road descends into Coldridge Valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14700 2 14722
Reset M 0 14701 1 14722
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14725
Name     &xWendigo Cave - Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A cave mouth gapes in the mountainside, icicles hanging from its rim like
fangs. An unnatural cold emanates from within, and massive clawed footprints
mark the snow. This is the lair of the dreaded wendigos—only the brave or
foolish enter here. The trail back to the pass lies &Yeast&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14721
Desc      The trail leads back to Coldridge Pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14726
Desc      The cave descends into frozen darkness.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14704 1 14725
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14726
Name     &xWendigo Cave - Frozen Tunnels&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Ice coats every surface of this frozen tunnel. Your breath crystallizes
instantly, and the cold saps the strength from your limbs. The bones of
unfortunate victims lie scattered on the floor, gnawed clean. Growls and
the scrape of claws echo from deeper within.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14725
Desc      The entrance lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14727
Desc      The tunnel continues deeper.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14704 2 14726
Reset O 0 14705 1 14726
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14727
Name     &xWendigo Cave - Old Icebeard's Lair&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     This vast frozen chamber is the domain of &WOld Icebeard&d, the most
ancient and terrible wendigo in all of Dun Morogh. Ice formations rise
like frozen trees, and the cold is so intense that even fire struggles
to burn. The massive creature watches from the shadows, its eyes gleaming
with predatory hunger.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14726
Desc      The frozen tunnels lie to the east.
~
