#ROOM
Vnum     14730
Name     &WDun Morogh - Brewnall Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road winds west from Kharanos through snow-covered hills. Brewnall
Village lies ahead, a small settlement known for its hops farms that
supply the Thunderbrew Distillery. The hills to the &Ynorth&d are rumored
to harbor Frostmane troll camps.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14710
Desc      The road leads back toward Kharanos.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14733
Desc      A trail leads into the troll-infested hills.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14731
Desc      The road continues toward Brewnall Village.
~
