Reset M 0 14723 2 14730
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14731
Name     &YBrewnall Village - East Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You enter &YBrewnall Village&d, a tiny farming community dedicated to
growing the hops and barley that make Thunderbrew Ale possible. Small
cottages with snow-covered roofs cluster around frozen fields. Despite
the cold, workers tend to winter preparations. The village center lies
to the &Ywest&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14730
Desc      The road leads back toward Kharanos.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14732
Desc      The village center lies ahead.
~
