#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14732
Name     &YBrewnall Village - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The small center of Brewnall Village consists of little more than a
well, a small shrine, and a general store. Life is hard here on the
frontier, but the villagers are proud of their contribution to dwarven
culture. The hop fields stretch to the &Ynorth&d, and a farmhouse stands
to the &Ysouth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14735
Desc      The hop fields lie to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14731
Desc      The east entrance lies behind you.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14736
Desc      A sturdy farmhouse stands to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14720 1 14732
Reset M 0 14721 2 14732
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14733
Name     &wFrostmane Territory - South Hills&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     You enter territory claimed by the &CFrostmane trolls&d. Crude totems of
bone and ice mark their boundaries, and the snow is stained with old
blood. Troll scouts watch from the ridges, and war drums echo in the
distance. The safe road lies to the &Ysouth&d, and the hills continue
&Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14734
Desc      The hills continue into troll territory.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14730
Desc      The road lies to the south.
~
