  Reset E 1 14707 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14734
Name     &CFrostmane Hold - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A crude palisade of sharpened logs surrounds the main &CFrostmane&d
encampment. Troll warriors patrol the perimeter, and smoke rises from
cooking fires within. Shrunken heads and Alliance banners hang from
poles as grim trophies. This is the heart of Frostmane power in Dun
Morogh.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14738
Desc      The main camp lies beyond the palisade.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14733
Desc      The hills lead back south.
~
