  Reset E 1 14706 1 16
Reset M 0 14707 2 14734
  Reset E 1 14707 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14735
Name     &YBrewnall Village - Hop Fields&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Even in winter, the frozen remnants of hop vines cling to wooden frames.
Come spring, these fields will burst with the plants that give Thunderbrew
Ale its distinctive flavor. Workers prepare the soil and repair frames
despite the cold. A trampled, snowy path leads northwest away from the
safety of the village.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14732
Desc      The village center lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction northwest~
ToRoom    14766
Desc      A treacherous path leading toward the irradiated ruins.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 2 14735
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14766
Name     &WPath to Gnomeregan&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The pristine white snow of Dun Morogh begins to take on a sickly, 
glowing green tint here. Discarded cogwheels, twisted metal pipes, and 
the faint sound of erratic mechanical whirring echo down the canyon. The 
massive, steel-vaulted entrance to the fallen gnome capital looms ahead.
~
Exit
Direction southeast~
ToRoom    14735
Desc      The path leads back to the safety of Brewnall Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14767
Desc      The loading elevator leading down into the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14713 3 14766
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14767
Name     &GGnomeregan - The Loading Bay&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand on a massive, rusted gear that serves as a makeshift 
loading bay. Toxic green sludge drips from the ceiling, and the air is 
thick with radiation and the smell of ozone. A swirling, mechanized 
portal hums violently here, sealing off the deeper, infected depths of 
the city. 
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14766
Desc      The path outside the vault.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14736
Name     &YBrewnall Village - Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This sturdy farmhouse belongs to one of Brewnall's founding families.
A fire crackles in the hearth, and the smell of cooking fills the air.
Simple but comfortable furniture fills the room, and farming tools hang
from hooks near the door.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14732
Desc      The village center lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 2 14736
Reset O 0 14714 2 14736
Reset O 0 14715 2 14736
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14738
Name     &CFrostmane Hold - Main Camp&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Crude tents and lean-tos fill this troll encampment. Warriors sharpen
weapons around smoking fires, and the witch doctors conduct dark rituals
in a sheltered corner. The stench of unwashed troll and rotting meat is
overpowering. The chieftain's hut lies to the &Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14739
Desc      The chieftain's hut looms ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14734
Desc      The entrance lies to the south.
~
