#ROOM
Vnum     14739
Name     &CFrostmane Hold - Chieftain's Hut&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The largest structure in the camp, this hut is draped with furs and
trophies of war. A fire pit smolders in the center, and crude weapons
line the walls. The Frostmane chieftain holds court here, planning
raids against the dwarven settlements.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14738
Desc      The main camp lies outside.
~
