#ROOM
Vnum     14740
Name     &WDun Morogh - Gol'Bolar Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road heads east from Kharanos toward the &YGol'Bolar Quarry&d, one
of Ironforge's primary sources of stone and ore. Trogg attacks have
made the journey increasingly dangerous. The road continues &Yeast&d,
and a trail branches &Ysouth&d toward Helm's Bed Lake.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14741
Desc      The road continues toward the quarry.
~
#ENDEXIT
