Reset M 0 14709 2 14740
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14741
Name     &YGol'Bolar Quarry - Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The entrance to &YGol'Bolar Quarry&d is marked by massive stone blocks
and rusting mining equipment. Once a thriving operation, the quarry has
been partially overrun by Stonesplinter troggs. Mountaineers guard the
perimeter, trying to hold back the infestation. The quarry continues
&Yeast&d and &Ysouth&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14742
Desc      The quarry continues to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14743
Desc      The main excavation lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14740
Desc      The road leads back west.
~
