#ROOM
Vnum     14742
Name     &YGol'Bolar Quarry - East Pit&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A deep pit has been carved into the mountainside, exposing rich veins
of copper and tin. Abandoned mining carts sit on rusted tracks, and
picks and shovels lie where workers dropped them when fleeing trogg
attacks. The creatures now claim this section of the quarry.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14741
Desc      The quarry entrance lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    14744
Desc      A ramp descends into the mine tunnels.
~
