#ROOM
Vnum     14743
Name     &YGol'Bolar Quarry - Main Excavation&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     This massive open pit is the heart of the quarry's operations. Terraced
walls descend deep into the earth, and tunnels branch off in several
directions. Fighting between dwarves and troggs has turned this into a
contested battleground.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14741
Desc      The quarry entrance lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    14744
Desc      A ramp descends into the mine tunnels.
~
