#ROOM
Vnum     14744
Name     &xGol'Bolar Quarry - Mine Tunnels&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Dark tunnels branch through the rock, following veins of ore deep into
the mountain. Troggs have made these passages their own, driving out the
dwarven miners. Their crude camps and foul refuse litter the floor. The
trogg leader is said to lurk in the deepest chambers.
~
Exit
Direction up~
ToRoom    14743
Desc      The ramp leads back up to the excavation.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14748
Desc      A tunnel leads deeper into trogg territory.
~
