#ROOM
Vnum     14745
Name     &CHelm's Bed Lake - North Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The frozen expanse of &CHelm's Bed Lake&d stretches before you, its
surface covered in thick ice. Fishermen have cut holes in the ice,
sitting patiently with their lines despite the cold. The Amberstill
Ranch is visible to the &Yeast&d, and the road lies to the &Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14740
Desc      The road lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14746
Desc      The path leads toward Amberstill Ranch.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14749
Desc      The lake shore continues south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 2 14745
Reset M 0 14723 3 14745
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14746
Name     &YAmberstill Ranch - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A sturdy wooden fence marks the boundary of &YAmberstill Ranch&d, the
finest ram breeding operation in Dun Morogh. You can see the main
farmhouse to the &Yeast&d and ram pens to the &Ysouth&d. The bleating of
rams and smell of hay fill the air.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14747
Desc      The farmhouse lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14765
Desc      The ram pens lie to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14745
Desc      The lake shore lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14721 2 14746
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14747
Name     &YAmberstill Ranch - Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This well-built farmhouse is the home of the Amberstill family, ram
breeders for generations. Trophies of prize-winning rams hang on the
walls, and the smell of hearty stew simmers from the kitchen. A fire
crackles warmly in the hearth.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14746
Desc      The ranch entrance lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
