#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14748
Name     &xGol'Bolar Quarry - Grik'nir's Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The deepest chamber of the quarry has been claimed by &RGrik'nir the
Cold&d, chieftain of the Stonesplinter troggs. Ice coats the walls despite
being deep underground, and the air is frigid. The massive trogg sits on
a throne of skulls and ore, his frozen club within easy reach.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14744
Desc      The tunnels lead back south.
~
