#ROOM
Vnum     14749
Name     &CHelm's Bed Lake - South Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The southern shore of the frozen lake is quieter, with fewer visitors.
Snow-covered pines line the water's edge, and a small shrine to the
ancestors sits on a rocky outcrop. The north shore lies back to the
&Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14745
Desc      The north shore lies ahead.
~
