#ROOM
Vnum     14750
Name     &WColdridge Valley - North Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     You descend into &CColdridge Valley&d, the sheltered vale where many
young dwarves begin their adventures. Despite being somewhat protected
from the worst weather, the valley is still bitterly cold. The settlement
of &YAnvilmar&d is visible to the &Ysouth&d. Coldridge Pass lies to the
&Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14722
Desc      The pass leads back north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14751
Desc      The road leads toward Anvilmar.
~
