#ROOM
Vnum     14751
Name     &WColdridge Valley - Valley Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road winds through the valley floor between snow-covered hills. Young
boars root through the snow, and the occasional rabbit darts across the
path. Anvilmar lies to the &Ysouth&d, and the valley continues &Ynorth&d. A
trail branches &Yeast&d toward the frozen lake.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14750
Desc      The valley continues north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14760
Desc      A trail leads toward Iceflow Lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14752
Desc      The road leads toward Anvilmar.
~
