#ROOM
Vnum     14752
Name     &YAnvilmar - North Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You approach &YAnvilmar&d, a small outpost that serves as the first line
of civilization for those venturing into Coldridge Valley. Stone walls
provide some protection, and Mountaineers patrol vigilantly. The main
square lies to the &Ysouth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14751
Desc      The valley road lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
