#ROOM
Vnum     14753
Name     &YAnvilmar - Main Square&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The center of Anvilmar is a small but busy square. A well provides water,
and a few merchant stalls offer basic supplies. The main building lies to
the &Ywest&d, and training grounds are to the &Yeast&d. The road continues
&Ysouth&d toward the Grizzled Den.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14752
Desc      The north gate lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
