#ROOM
Vnum     14754
Name     &YAnvilmar - Main Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This stone building serves as the administrative center of Anvilmar. A
large hearth keeps the interior warm, and maps of the valley cover the
walls. The local commander coordinates defense efforts against trogg
incursions from here. Supplies are stacked along one wall.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14753
Desc      The main square lies outside.
~
