#ROOM
Vnum     14755
Name     &YAnvilmar - Training Grounds&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Training dummies and weapon racks fill this open area where new recruits
learn the basics of combat. Veteran Mountaineers put trainees through
their paces, teaching them to fight with rifle, axe, and hammer. The
main square lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14753
Desc      The main square lies to the west.
~
