Vnum     14756
Name     &WColdridge Valley - Southern Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road leads south from Anvilmar into wilder territory. Trogg totems
become more frequent, warning of the creatures' presence. The infamous
&RGrizzled Den&d, a cave complex overrun by troggs, lies to the &Yeast&d.
Anvilmar lies to the &Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14753
Desc      Anvilmar lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
