#ROOM
Vnum     14757
Name     &yThe Grizzled Den - Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A dark cave mouth opens in the hillside, decorated with crude trogg
totems and the bones of unfortunate victims. This is &RThe Grizzled Den&d,
home to a large tribe of Stonesplinter troggs. Growls and the clatter of
stone tools echo from within. The valley road lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14756
Desc      The valley road lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
