Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Rough tunnels wind through the rock, littered with refuse and gnawed
bones. Trogg guards lurk in the shadows, ready to alert the tribe to
intruders. The stench of the creatures is nearly overwhelming. The cave
continues &Yeast&d, and the entrance lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
