Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A large cavern serves as the heart of the trogg lair. Crude fire pits
cast flickering shadows, and troggs go about their primitive existence—
crafting weapons, squabbling over food, and grunting in their guttural
language. Tunnels branch &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d to sleeping areas.
~
