Vnum     14760
Name     &CIceflow Lake - Western Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The frozen expanse of &CIceflow Lake&d stretches before you, a smaller
and more isolated body of water than Helm's Bed Lake. Few venture here,
making it a haven for wildlife—and occasionally trolls. The valley road
lies to the &Ywest&d, and the shore continues &Yeast&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14761
Desc      The shore continues around the lake.
~
