#ROOM
Vnum     14761
Name     &CIceflow Lake - Northern Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The northern shore of Iceflow Lake is marked by a crashed flying machine,
its twisted metal half-buried in the snow. A gnome pilot works frantically
on repairs, surrounded by scattered parts. The shore continues &Ywest&d
and &Yeast&d.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    14762
Desc      The shore continues east.
~
