#ROOM
Vnum     14762
Name     &CIceflow Lake - Eastern Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The eastern shore of the lake is wilder and more remote. Animal tracks
crisscross the snow, and the occasional howl echoes from the nearby hills.
The shore continues back to the &Ywest&d.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    14761
Desc      The shore continues west.
~
