#ROOM
Vnum     14763
Name     &xThe Grizzled Den - North Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     This smaller chamber serves as a sleeping area for part of the trogg
tribe. Crude bedding of moss and animal skins covers the floor, and
the stench is indescribable. A few troggs rest here between raids on
the surface.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    14759
Desc      The central chamber lies to the south.
~
