#ROOM
Vnum     14764
Name     &xThe Grizzled Den - South Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Another sleeping area, this chamber is slightly warmer due to a natural
hot spring that bubbles in one corner. The troggs have fouled the water
with their refuse, but the warmth makes this a prized location in the
tribe.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14759
Desc      The central chamber lies to the north.
~
