#ROOM
Vnum     14765
Name     &YAmberstill Ranch - Ram Pens&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Sturdy wooden pens contain the famous Amberstill rams. These magnificent
beasts have thick wool and curling horns, bred for strength and endurance.
Handlers move among them, checking their health and preparing them for
sale or service. The ranch entrance lies to the &Ynorth&d.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    14746
Desc      The ranch entrance lies to the north.
~
